comment:
* Class to hold deletion related request. This is an internal class for communication between the
 * {@link MeasurementManager} and {@link IMeasurementService} impl.
 *
 * @hide

methods.name: public int describeContents()
methods.comment: For Parcelable, no special marshalled objects.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel out, int flags)
methods.comment: For Parcelable, write out to a Parcel in particular order.

methods.name: public List<Uri> getOriginUris()
methods.comment: * Publisher/Advertiser Origins for which data should be deleted. These will be matched as-is.

methods.name: public List<Uri> getDomainUris()
methods.comment:
* Publisher/Advertiser domains for which data should be deleted. These will be pattern matched
     * with regex SCHEME://(.*\.|)SITE .

methods.name: public Instant getStart()
methods.comment:
* Instant in time the deletion starts, or {@link java.time.Instant#MIN} if starting at the
     * oldest possible time.

methods.name: public Instant getEnd()
methods.comment:
* Instant in time the deletion ends, or {@link java.time.Instant#MAX} if ending at the most
     * recent time.

methods.name: public String getAppPackageName()
methods.comment: Package name of the app used for the deletion.

methods.name: public String getSdkPackageName()
methods.comment: Package name of the sdk used for the deletion.

methodNames: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel out, int flags)
